wiki.content: Adele successfuly brings together the playful and seductive with this classic-contemporary piece. The instrumental makes in soft and mellow, while her soulful vocals add the right kind of spice to make this song an all around, feel-good, masterpiece!!! According to the Daydreamer Songfacts, this song is about Adele falling for a bisexual male friend.
